HOW TO USE THIS TEMPLATE:

If you fork or use this template:
1. Delete all personal content in the content/ directory
2. Replace with your own YAML configurations, images, and content
3. Keep the LICENSE file and code attribution
4. The template structure, code, and design are free to use and modify

The template is designed to make content replacement easy - just edit the YAML
files and add your own content!
